@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Weight Ticket Item Tote'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define view entity zpr_i_item_tote
  as select from zpr_tb_wt_tote
  association to parent ZPR_I_ITEM as _Item on  $projection.Werks   = _Item.Werks
                                            and $projection.Wtktno  = _Item.Wtktno
                                            and $projection.Wtktitm = _Item.Wtktitm
  association [0..1] to ZPR_I_MATERIAL      as _Material on  $projection.Totetype  = _Material.Material
                                                         and _Material.Language = $session.system_language
  association [0..1] to ZPR_I_UOM         as _Measure1 on  $projection.Tuom = _Measure1.Measure
                                                      and _Measure1.Language      = $session.system_language
  association [1..1] to ZPR_I_UOM         as _Measure2 on  $projection.TWeightUom = _Measure2.Measure
                                                      and _Measure2.Language      = $session.system_language
{
  key werks    as Werks,
  key wtktno   as Wtktno,
  key wtktitm  as Wtktitm,
  key toteitem as Toteitem,
      tote     as Tote,
      totetype as Totetype,
      quantity as Quantity,
      tweight  as Tweight,
      tuom     as Tuom,
      twtuom   as TWeightUom,
      _Item,
      _Item._Header,
      _Item.Werks as IWerks,
      _Item.Wtktno as IWtktno,
      _Material,
      _Measure1.MeasureName as MName1,
      _Measure2.MeasureName as MName2
     
}
